15:34.739 --> 15:36.820
Balik nanti ada bencana.

15:41.940 --> 15:42.619
Mak cik.

15:43.499 --> 15:44.060
Mak cik.

15:44.379 --> 15:44.940
Tak.

15:45.379 --> 15:47.220
Ada orang buat kain rentang di dataran.

15:47.220 --> 15:48.460
Beri telur percuma lagi.

15:49.899 --> 15:51.340
Baru kena pukul, berani datang lagi.

15:51.340 --> 15:52.460
Betul-betul berani.

15:52.460 --> 15:53.180
