20:16.300 --> 20:17.459
Bagaimana kami nak percaya kamu?

20:17.459 --> 20:18.300
Kenapa begini?

20:18.300 --> 20:19.540
Tak apa.

20:19.780 --> 20:20.580
Lagipun, kami

20:20.580 --> 20:21.500
